{"type": "article", "id": 41394, "title": "让字母变成画，它里面可以装的东西超出你的想象｜这个设计了不起", "description": "每个周末，《好奇心日报》都会找个主题为你寻找精彩设计。", "date": "2017-05-28T23:08:25Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 40929, "name": "文字设计"}, {"id": 40930, "name": "Kjosk Collective"}, {"id": 40931, "name": "Deepblue Networks"}, {"id": 40932, "name": "David Doran"}, {"id": 40933, "name": "Keisuke Terashima"}, {"id": 40934, "name": "Pawel Nolbert"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 9, "praise_count": 167, "image": "img/article/article_show/20170528022124A28tiWjLyIlNzCSc.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #323333} p.p4 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p5 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #323333} p.p6 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #323333; min-height: 25.0px} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font-kerning: none; color: #363636} span.s3 {font-kerning: none; color: #323333} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><p class=\"\">作为设计的基础元素，文字和图像既独立又共存。在文字设计中，一部分平面设计师就通过将文字图像化的方法，达成了图文并茂的效果。本周的推荐就是这些既是文字也是图像的设计。</p><h3>Deepblue Networks by Kjosk Collective</h3><p>想要了解一家公司不一定非得通过大段的文字，德国设计团队 <a href=\"http://www.kjosk.de/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Kjosk Collective</a> 只用了八个<a href=\"https://www.behance.net/gallery/23304545/DAS-KREATIVE-HAUS\" rel=\"nofollow\">字母</a>就为创意公司 <a href=\"http://www.db-n.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Deepblue Networks</a> 完成了一次成功的形象推广。他们以公司实际所在的大楼为灵感，将建筑造型与公司名中的每个字母融合在了一起，并且在里面加入了以员工的真实经历为原型设计的小人。无论是对潜在的未来员工还是客户而言，这种自我介绍的方式显然要有趣得多，更具亲和力。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170528022433MhxZbk8LpHnU0VTq.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.158333\" data-format=\"gif\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170528022435OVKTQULJwgopE7Xl.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.158333\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170528022435aBvJXRk7bZdl38s4.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.158333\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170528022433RAr8T5WkYZH7Fcnl.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.158333\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170528022433Ourbt3lFqaRLGA8c.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.158333\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170528022435CB6Ejkdex5miYUPI.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.146667\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Alphabet Cities by David Doran</h3><p>如果你喜欢旅行，又对文字设计感兴趣，由英国插画家 <a href=\"https://daviddoran.co.uk/\" rel=\"nofollow\">David Doran</a> 绘制的 <a href=\"https://daviddoran.co.uk/alphabet-cities/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Alphabet Cities: Around the World in 32 Pull-out Prints</a> 会让你一饱眼福。Doran 参考了 20 世纪早期旅行海报的风格，将城市的首字母与充满生活气息的画面自然地融为一体，仿佛不经意间完成的精妙抓拍。书中的每一幅插画都配有相关的城市趣闻，这是它的<a href=\"https://www.amazon.co.uk/Alphabet-Cities-Around-Pull-out-Prints/dp/0753545403\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价为 18.98 英镑。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170528022414Csf8bg7polaRnzvP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.414000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170528022414UGSEgvZNs0lo47Fk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.370000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170528022414rXP8Z9cSKg7pd64I.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.376000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170528022415oDMV3Jt4BlZcNTAP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.376000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Skatepark Font by Keisuke Terashima</h3><p>经过公园时，你留心过那些热衷于挑战高难度动作的滑板爱好者吗？日本平面设计师 <a href=\"http://www.keisuketerashima.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Keisuke Terashima</a> 以平日里观察到的那些流畅帅气的动作和公园本身的构造为灵感，创作了一套由动态的橙色滑板点缀的文字&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/skateparkfont/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Skatepark Font</a>。如果你喜欢这种风格，可以从 <a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/app/skatepark-font/id1200182785\" rel=\"nofollow\">App Store</a> 中下载到它的 iMessage 贴纸。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170528022316rtU1CT8Zz6kcFeD3.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"gif\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170528022316RYdIBzgG5q3xkbiu.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170528022321MyzlWnYFt4eca13k.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Conceptual Alphabet by Mike Karolos</h3><p><a href=\"http://www.36daysoftype.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">36 Days of Type</a> 是一个已经举办了四届的文字挑战，参与的设计师需要在连续 36 天的时间内为 10 个数字和 26 个英语字母设计一套独具特色的字体。现居雅典的英国设计师 <a href=\"http://www.smirapdesigns.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Mike Karolos</a> 选择了他擅长描绘的几何形状，将每个<a href=\"http://www.smirapdesigns.com/conceptual-alphabet\" rel=\"nofollow\">字母</a>藏进了以其开头的联想词插画中，就像是一套单词卡片。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170528022344xIStzL3vrdY5OkZU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.437500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170528022344gOUMqWL8AVIRkuGi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.193750\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170528022345UYXONBRTQs41lC7t.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.193750\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170528022344gBfXxEcnj2OHC9Pe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.193750\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170528022344kSZyhmJOKHwBVg1c.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.193750\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170528022345Uk8K4A01XQNIMj9q.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.193750\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>A to Z by Sebastian Deredas</h3><p>来自波兰的 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/sebastianderedas\" rel=\"nofollow\">Sebastian Deredas</a> 是一名 3D 艺术家，他为 36 Days of Type 创作的 26 个立体字母并没有遵循统一的风格，而是尽可能地创造差异、体现出字母背后的故事。除了包豪斯（B）、迪士尼（D）、facebook（F）这类能够一眼认出出处的字母之外，Deredas 还打造了不少考验知识储备和想象力的“难题”。你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.behance.net/gallery/50397997/36-Days-of-Type-04\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>查看所有字母的灵感来源。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170528022205dUKD3jChfcYxGuTZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170528022209GzrEUL7xd60vpb2y.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170528022202IWcJQpLYyD1XaZKS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201705280222051s7fluqYQwn8ghbA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170528022205hnLGK3oj5ImTfyF7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170528022202v76rqKgd8ucI3Pk2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Atypical by Pawel Nolbert</h3><p class=\"\">当你第一眼看到由波兰视觉艺术家 <a href=\"http://www.nolbert.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Pawel Nolbert</a> 创作的立体文字&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.behance.net/gallery/16919659/Atypical\" rel=\"nofollow\">Atypical</a> 时，或许会认为这只是电脑特效。实际上，这些虚实难辨的字母是 Nolbert 利用颜料和柔软的塑料板亲手打造的一场视觉错觉。你可以通过<a href=\"https://society6.com/hellocolor/prints\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>购买到这些海报，售价从 27 美元起。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170528022234nR5D0oXMQz4N8hKI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.414667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170528022230KUCpTZOPFSQ2BfXw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.414667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170528022234QcVxXenBK5IoPrlS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.414667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170528022230YdfeDo580zhL9kGJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170528022230phujYVdMTxmW72B5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201705280222349aAS02GbwDy7x8Tv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}